<p>M&#7897;t b&aacute;o c&aacute;o &#273;&#432;&#7907;c T&#7893; ch&#7913;c s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng Anh qu&#7889;c ( PHE) c&ocirc;ng b&#7889; h&ocirc;m nay &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;a ra k&#7871;t lu&#7853;nthu&#7889;c l&aacute; &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917; (e-ciggarette hay e-cig) &iacute;t nguy h&#7841;i &#273;&#7871;n s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e h&#417;n 95% so v&#7899;i thu&#7889;c l&aacute; truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng. Th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o &#273;&oacute;, n&oacute; c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c xem l&agrave; m&#7897;t gi&#7843;i ph&aacute;p ti&#7873;m n&#259;ng gi&uacute;p ng&#432;&#7901;i nghi&#7879;n b&#7887; thu&#7889;c l&aacute; v&agrave; trong t&#432;&#417;ng lai D&#7883;ch v&#7909; s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e qu&#7889;c gia (NHS) c&#7911;a Anh c&oacute; th&#7875; k&ecirc; &#273;&#417;n nh&#432; m&#7897;t thi&#7871;t b&#7883; d&#432;&#7907;c ph&#7849;m th&ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng.</p>
<p>Gi&aacute;o s&#432; Ann McNeil &#273;&#7871;n t&#7915; &#273;&#7841;i h&#7885;c King, London cho bi&#7871;t: &ldquo;E-cig c&oacute; th&#7875; s&#7869; k&#7867; thay &#273;&#7893;i cu&#7897;c ch&#417;i trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e c&ocirc;ng &#273;&#7891;ng, c&#7909; th&#7875; h&#417;n l&agrave; l&agrave;m gi&#7843;m nh&#7919;ng nguy c&#417; v&#7873; s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e g&acirc;y ra b&#7903;i thu&#7889;c l&aacute;.&rdquo; Theo nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u c&#7911;a PHE th&igrave; c&oacute; g&#7847;n 1 n&#7917;a d&acirc;n s&#7889; Anh (44,8%) kh&ocirc;ng nh&#7853;n th&#7913;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c r&#7857;ng vi&#7879;c h&uacute;t hay ng&#7917;i h&#417;i kh&oacute;i t&#7915; e-cig &iacute;t nguy hi&#7875;m h&#417;n so v&#7899;i thu&#7889;c l&aacute; truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng. Tr&ecirc;n th&#7921;c t&#7871;, ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i cho r&#7857;ng e-cig c&#361;ng nguy hi&#7875;m kh&ocirc;ng k&eacute;m thu&#7889;c l&aacute; truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng v&agrave; 22,1% d&acirc;n s&#7889; v&#7851;n gi&#7919; quan &#273;i&#7875;m n&agrave;y trong n&#259;m 2015, t&#259;ng t&#7915; 8,1% so v&#7899;i n&#259;m 2013. PHE kh&ocirc;ng g&#7907;i &yacute; r&#7857;ng e-cig ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n an to&agrave;n nh&#432;ng tin r&#7857;ng nh&#7853;n th&#7913;c c&#7911;a c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng c&oacute; v&#7873; e-cig c&oacute; th&#7875; khi&#7871;n nh&#7919;ng ai nghi&#7879;n thu&#7889;c c&oacute; th&#7875; chuy&#7875;n sang e-cig v&agrave; sau c&ugrave;ng l&agrave; b&#7887; ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n th&oacute;i quen n&agrave;y. Gi&aacute;o s&#432; Kevin Fenton, gi&aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c ph&ograve;ng s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e v&agrave; an sinh t&#7841;i PHE cho bi&#7871;t: &ldquo;Nh&#7919;ng d&#7883;ch v&#7909; cai nghi&#7879;n thu&#7889;c l&aacute; &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; h&#7895; tr&#7907; cho ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng e-cig trong h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh b&#7887; t&#7915; b&#7887; thu&#7889;c l&aacute; ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n.&rdquo;</p>
